      <text>Please treat the 'Off' in the sliders as '0%' also slider is percent reduction of selected speaker</text>
    </label>
    <label>
      <text>If silder is at 'Off' read as 0% reduction, ie both speakers are 100% of volume setting as set on Volume tab</text>
    </label>
    <label>
      <text>If Speaker 1 selected and silder is at '50%', speaker 1 is half the volume as speaker 2 and speaker 2 is as set on Volume tab</text>
    </label>
    <label>
      <text>If Speaker 2 selected and silder is at '100%', speaker 2 is silent and speaker 1 is as set on Volume tab</text>
